column5: Just fished the lake winnipeg for the last 3 days, the water clarity is still coming around but will still did very well. If anyone is interested in renting a 4 bedroom house approx. 15 minutes to the mouth of lake winnipeg send me a private message.Happy New Year to everyone.
Thanks for the report..were you the person I met at Pro Am Sports??? last Monday.. Steve
That's the guy you met at ProAm tackle. Bryan is on vacation down south & he well be back in 2 weeks?
